            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1695718546606-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1695718546606-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dip the<strong> flattened</strong> <strong>chicken</strong> in the<strong> lemon oil</strong> then coat with the<strong> breadcrumbs</strong> until both sides are well coated</p><p>Add the<strong> coated</strong> <strong>chicken</strong> to one side of an oiled baking tray</p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 25 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>chicken Milanese</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1695718551037-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1695718551037-x400.jpg",
