            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dissolve the <strong>chicken stock mix</strong> in 150ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> [250ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>After an initial 25 min, remove the tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> of vegetables from the oven and crush the <strong>cooked tomato wedges</strong> with the back of a fork</p><p>Pour over the<strong> chicken stock</strong> and top with the<strong> trimmed green beans</strong></p><p>Return the tray to the oven for a final 12-15 min or until the beans are tender and the stock has reduced</p>",
      "order": 6,
